column2: select a.artistid, a.name as artist, count (t.trackid) as numClassical from chinook.artist a inner join chinook.album b on b.artistid = a.artistid inner join chinook.track t on t.albumid = b.albumid inner join chinook.Genre g on g.genreid = t.genreid and g.name = # group by a.artistid, a.name order by a.name
